## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023, and the rapidly evolving nature of drug addiction treatment and policy. Additionally, the focus was primarily on English-language sources, which may not capture global perspectives on the issue. Further research could explore more diverse cultural and international approaches to drug addiction.

